{"tid":28926,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［收費］政府計劃增加頻譜牌照費用","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T11:01:25.000Z","uid":11084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15a3623fd78b8e5067542202130c6516de5d3a11","tid":28926,"uid":11084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"香港電訊(<a href=\"http://06823.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06823.HK&d=nRBCArb6Vd4Iu1%2ByI8vYjwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=46fc55e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06823.HK</a>)委託調查：九成市民不知政府擬調升頻譜費用 <br />\n2016-11-28 17:43:10 <br />\n香港電訊(<a href=\"http://06823.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F06823.HK&d=nRBCArb6Vd4Iu1%2ByI8vYjwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=46fc55e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">06823.HK</a>)委託研究機構「政策二十一」進行一項消費者調查，了解公眾對政府就頻譜指配期屆滿後安排及頻譜使用費諮詢的認知程度，及消費者對政府計劃調高頻譜費及其他相關議題的意見。調查結果顯示，88.1%的受訪者不知悉有關諮詢；91.6%受訪者不知悉政府有計劃調升流動網絡商須繳付的頻譜費用；70.3%受訪者指政府毋須以上調頻譜價格來增加庫房收入。調查於11月12日至15日進行，成功訪問了1,019人。<br />\n<br />\n另香港電訊亦委託電訊顧問公司Network Strategies 進行研究。Network Strategies董事兼創辦人Suella Hansen認為，通訊事務管理局建議參考三次拍賣以決定將來重新分配頻譜的參考價格水平，以這個價格水平來作為底價或定價可能會導致人為地推高頻譜使用費，令市場可能出現扭曲效應。<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊無線業務策略及核心網絡主管黃錦恆在一個論壇上表示，流動數據服務錄得爆發性增長，並預期會持續快速增長。頻譜是一項關鍵的元素，以滿足這些需求及進一步拓展服務。國際電信聯盟已指出部分頻帶可釋出作流動服務之用。當中包括數碼紅利(694至790兆赫)及42頻段(3400至3600兆赫)的頻譜。這些頻帶應提供予香港營運商使用，以免香港落後於其他國家。(ay/da)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=nRBCArb6Vd4Iu1%2ByI8vYjwv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=f14c9fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"c4df4a0d05edc1bf3e97242f4b706d9bd5276f84","tid":28926,"uid":11084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"樣樣都加價淨係人工唔加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0c49bdcd16b28ceced2623682517dd7b3a7289","tid":28926,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"記憶中政府向電訊商收既牌費係每人<span style=\"color: red;\">每年</span>$18<br />\n電訊商向用家收既牌費係每人<span style=\"color: red;\">每月</span>$18<br />\n大家畀既牌費根本係畀電訊商既貼士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67594734ce5a09ddec082e6613e39e42ea856a8d","tid":28926,"uid":11084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"冇辦法，比人&quot;禁&quot;住搶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e563c0bc9e07b5370cb4c8434e690d0f4c6dd75b","tid":28926,"uid":55087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"憨鳩政苦比機會奸商濫收人錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}